<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226947>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Phylogenetic hypothesis derived from maximum likelihood analysis based on a fragment of the 16 S mitochondrial gene (540 bp). The sequence of the species described here is referred to \" Podocoryna loyola Brazil. \" The numbers above and below the branches support values are obtained per 100 bootstrap replicates." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226947/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

